OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fshowery night for many with hail and
OL,7,Fthunder in places, accompanied by gale
OL,8,Fforce winds in exposed northern and
OL,9,Fwestern areas. Clearer spells towards
OL,10,Fthe south and east, where less
OL,11,Fblustery. Most places escaping a frost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FSunday will bring a mix of
OL,14,Fsunshine and showers, the showers
OL,15,Flocally heavy with hail and thunder.
OL,16,FRemaining windy in the north with
OL,17,Fcoastal gales, and feeling rather cool
OL,18,Foverall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
